{"tid":2170537,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：我絕對反對港獨，台獨，贊成華夏邦聯，取消主權國，重建周朝，並邀請日本、韓國、越南和新加坡加盟！","createTime":"2020-08-23T10:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T15:08:33.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"01be6b6e7764c483cb80b9c15c2b1575dfea576f","tid":2170537,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:31:53.000Z","msg":"陳雲：星期日講道。主權國家的禍害。中世紀的黑死病（腺體鼠疫）殺人無數，但沒有引起封城，而是引起逃亡及社會開放，引起文藝復興與宗教改革，引起古希臘美學和思想的復活，也引起歐洲人對中亞、印度和中國文明的興趣。因為當時並無作惡多端的主權國家，只是王國、諸侯國和商人自治城邦，非常多元化的統治。黑死病的瘟疫來了，這些統治的王公大臣是要開放求生，不是求封閉集權。<br />\n現在，主權國家&mdash;&mdash;即使是幾弱小的主權國家，只要政府下令封閉海關，我們就連沒有欄柵隔開的邊界也不敢跨越。在中世紀，沒有士兵會在這種瘟疫的時候效忠王侯而守住邊關的，窮人可以隨意湧入富裕的城市求生。<br />\n主權國家是人類社會的萬惡之源。我寫《香港城邦論》、《城邦主權論》，是人類文明和政治經濟學的反省，只是用香港做例子。<br />\n想一想，沒有主權國家來裝載共產主義，共產主義只是巴黎公社一群愛好讀書的文青的同人運動，好像香港的菜園村運動，斷不會引起人類一半被勞役的災難，而且會生產良心食品。<br />\n基於這樣的深奧原因，我絕對反對港獨，也不贊成台灣獨立，我是贊成華夏邦聯，取消主權國的存在，重建周朝的天下，並且邀請日本、韓國、越南和新加坡來加盟！這是我遭受深層國家迫害的根本原因。<br />\n其他的，我在其他地方寫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x8R21jJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx8R21jJ.png&h=fa0825a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a744a539939863b34f466423213f7fad65149c6c","tid":2170537,"uid":171389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:44:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 而家先黎淆底<br />\n熱狗死全家"},{"pid":"460639c23f4508b4167ae7e21a29fad2b9bebd76","tid":2170537,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kZrB5Vw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkZrB5Vw.png&h=b7410f19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳云根的港獨三變臉<br />\n<a href=\"http://plastichk.blogspot.com/2016/09/blog-post_6.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplastichk.blogspot.com%2F2016%2F09%2Fblog-post_6.html%3Fm%3D1&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTM%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=32a2c7aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://plastichk.blogspot.com/2016/09/blog-post_6.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"d2b27cf000309326c84743a07440a34dddfd350a","tid":2170537,"uid":36861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T11:00:16.000Z","msg":"可不可以捉左佢，會用fb既痴線佬。"},{"pid":"59c2fdb870e8d1c4446418e877f90974c1141b3f","tid":2170537,"uid":22068,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T11:11:07.000Z","msg":"老老實實，你唔認同也好，佢係始終如一咁講華夏邦聯，後期先俾人話係華夏膠。"},{"pid":"3c0264307f21445af9e623d803769c6b73993d0c","tid":2170537,"uid":282757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T11:31:48.000Z","msg":"到底邊個逼害我地嘅國屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44ab7dc02d04fcc000929adb61be32fe446f9c2","tid":2170537,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3c0264307f21445af9e623d803769c6b73993d0c","tid":2170537,"uid":282757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T11:31:48.000Z","msg":"到底邊個逼害我地嘅國屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T11:36:34.000Z","msg":"陳雲根 被「民意」迫害<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/new-east-01_cCc71_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fnew-east-01_cCc71_1200x0.png&h=608ed7e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"659fb2e5d51691c9b64d100c18d061e20c21ceda","tid":2170537,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T11:42:40.000Z","msg":"人地elon musk上緊火星弱智支那人仲係到對住周朝打J。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560f6bb3f574d1cf9c14acf7407a8408ac365727","tid":2170537,"uid":312404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23